summary: WHILE PULLING INTO PARKING SPACE, HORN SUDDENLY BLOWS, WIPERS AND WASHERS COME ON, LIGHTS COME ONCAR BUCKS. BROUGHT TO DEALER KEPT FOR 3 DAYS, NO ANSWER. 3 DAYS LATER CAR PARKED HORN BLOWS WIPERS ON, DOORS LOCK.  2 DAYS AFTER CAR PARKED SAME THING. DEALER CAN FIND NO CODES.  REPEAT OF SAME INCIDENTS FROM 8/20/14,  SAME RESPONSE FROM DEALER.
